    "Currently, only less than half of papers include an evaluation, a minority of which with a control group.",
    "Preservation was the area of application with the fewest evaluations and the highest percentage of low-quality assessments.",
    "It also had the lowest sample size and fewer complex evaluations.",
    "The predominant evaluation purpose in this domain was almost exclusively Usability and User Experience.",
    "These results could be attributed to the fact that Preservation lacks a defined target audience."
